n = 128 (0x80) -> chunks: [0x00, 0x01]. i=1 -> b=0x81. i=0 -> b=0x00. 
result: 0x81, 0x00. Correct.
n = 16383 (0x3FFF) -> chunks: [0x7F, 0x7F]. i=1 -> 0xFF, i=0 -> 0x7F. 
